"},{"pid":"3551f39b39fb7ba147ef22db02e3f3a8e5b792f4","tid":1219302,"uid":169639,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:35:44.000Z","msg":"最後果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪同香港某些犬隻一樣唔識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22e71e42453b3c84dbca0d1cd14cd512599db85","tid":1219302,"uid":137233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:36:25.000Z","msg":"暗示直接一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd698e4506ba1b5eb363bc0b24b7811ae1b0da7","tid":1219302,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九唔搭八"},{"pid":"cfb0da1b4f9340f976c7426c6a9efe711d49d29a","tid":1219302,"uid":6261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:38:39.000Z","msg":"最後個句點搞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8d76790afa24177ffc2c111e12e26f5274acd2","tid":1219302,"uid":33825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚亂呀 師父"},{"pid":"a8dfccdfe55746170bf67d7438471903a5b8a479","tid":1219302,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"12ed21aa7b503caecae253973c7507b4c041a10a","tid":1219302,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:07:58.000Z","msg":"【相信賣菜郎、相信民主制度、相信中華民國】<br />\n<br />\n那天第一時間被問到「反送中」的問題，因為沒有掌握完整的訊息，所以我很誠實地說我不知道、不曉得。對此，我不推諉，也不迴避。<br />\n<br />\n中華民國是一個主權獨立的國家，我們的未來是握在每一位中華民國國民的手中。所以，台灣根本不存在一國兩制的問題，因為，只要中華民國國民不要，誰都沒有辦法把一國兩制強加在我們身上。<br />\n<br />\n過去幾十年來我們都生活在自由民主的青天白日滿地紅國度之中，民主和自由早已存在我們每一刻生活、每一口呼吸之中，更早已深植你我的生命。我從來不懷疑這塊土地對於民主自由價值的堅持。<br />\n<br />\n因為對於民主自由的堅持，我們支持香港的民主制度，我們關心反送中運動的民眾，但是我們捍衛、並且珍視的民主價值，不是藉著消費反送中運動，拿來做為打擊異己和爭取選票的工具。<br />\n<br />\n我會繼續堅定地捍衛中華民國，捍衛台灣的民主制度，捍衛台灣的生活方式。<br />\n<br />\n支持九二共識！反對台灣獨立！不接受一國兩制！<br />\n<br />\n#相信賣菜郎<br />\n#不接受一國兩制<br />\n#堅持民主自由<br />\n#相信中華民國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0ao3Ly.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0ao3Ly.jpg&h=5e7e9c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2461318357438647&amp;id=1863023523934803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2461318357438647%26id%3D1863023523934803&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=0004d4e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2461318357438647&amp;id=1863023523934803</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d42af636049f1478dc63e53637b550355c55085","tid":1219302,"uid":167186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:40:48.000Z","msg":"難怪光頭 做得牆頭草多"},{"pid":"436f18e4e7a0bc863825c2a38afc50b3658eccb8","tid":1219302,"uid":41411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:43:31.000Z","msg":"本身佢係台灣都比人反緊<br />\n香港單野更多人反佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47be71608cdae400f182a70f78ed5bfb154fe6a","tid":1219302,"uid":11417,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:49:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0514196fa8257aa897b3a6caef0d5e9776f62baa","tid":1219302,"uid":155133,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:49:35.000Z","msg":"九二共識係共產黨話係一國兩制姐<br />\n台灣理鳩你咩"},{"pid":"96890cae6fdc6b7e3bd32ae23e2ca329b5bfbd09","tid":1219302,"uid":135313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:49:43.000Z","msg":"